State Bank of India wants to calculate the simple interest on savings accounts. The 
bank offers a principal amount of â‚¹50,000 at an annual interest rate of 5.5% for a 
time period of 3 years. Write a program to calculate and display the simple interest. 
Code:  
        //Practical 3: Calculate Simple Interest For Given Value. 
 
 
#include<stdio.h> 
void main() 
{ 
    float Principal_Amount; 
    float Interest_Rate; 
    float Time_Period; 
 
            // Given Value 
 
            Principal_Amount=50000; 
            Interest_Rate=0.055; 
            Time_Period=3; 
 
            // Print Simple Interest 
 
     printf("Your Simple Interest=%f\n\n\n\n\n\n\n",Principal_Amount*Interest_Rate* 
Time_Period); 
 
printf("24ce032_TARANG"); 
   
} 

